The dates at which Horace's poems were written are in . some instances easily ascertained‚ in others will always re- main matters of doubtful conjecture. In disputed cases, the two extremes of the dates which have been proposed by scholars, or at least of the most plausible ones, are given in the notes, directly aster the caption of each poem.
